channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: Pharmacy leaders urge people not to buy fake weight-loss jabs online following shortages of Ozempic
item.description: The weight-loss injections have become very popular, with social media showing before and after pictures of fat loss, and some celebrities endorsing their use.

item.title: The 7ft tall dinosaur statue that is so big you can see it on Google Maps
item.description: How many times have you come across a 7ft tall dinosaur while checking out your old street or hometown?

item.title: Horoscopes today: Daily star sign predictions from Russell Grant on August 5
item.description: Today's horoscope will see one star sign move on to something new, while another will be committed to solving a relationship issue. These are your Monday horoscopes.

item.title: Meet the man who builds giant versions of household items, because why not?
item.description: Steve Wainwright said his retirement from the ambulance service first prompted him to take on some ‘creative’ building projects.

item.title: Princess Beatrice's husband broke major royal tradition thanks to Meghan Markle
item.description: Princess Beatrice's husband Edoardo Mapelli Mozzi joined the royals at Sandringham in 2019 for Christmas - and it was all thanks to a tradition that was allowed to be broken for Meghan Markle

item.title: Average price of car insurance falls for the first time in two years following astronomical price hikes
item.description: The cost of insuring a motor vehicle over the last two years has been astronomical with many motorists left struggling to pay the high premiums - but it looks as if the prices are finally beginning to fall.

item.title: Prince William and Kate Middleton altered Royal children's future with one key change
item.description: Prince William and Kate Middleton have definitely made their children their number one priority and now Royal expert Jennie Bond, believes one crucial change from the couple has altered the children's future forever
